## The bill object

> Sample Response

```json
{
  "balance": 100,
  "dueDate": "<%= config.futureDate %>",
  "status": {
    "type": "upcoming",
    "text": "<%= config.futureStatus %>",
    "image": "<%= config.statusSvg %>"
  },
  "settings": {
    "autoPay": true 
  }
}
```

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`balance` | Current bill balance.
`dueDate` | Current bill due date.
`lastPaidAmount` | Amount of last payment.
`lastPaidOn` | Date of last payment.
`status` | Status of the bill.
`status.type` | Type of bill status. Possible values are `syncing`, `overdue`, `authenticate`, `hold`, `upcoming`, `pending`, `paid`.
`status.text` | Helper text that describes the status type. Possible values are `Syncing`, `Tap to fix`, `Due XXX X`, `Overdue`, `Pending`, `Paid`.
`status.image` | URL of the status svg.
`reason` | Reason the bill is on hold.
`settings` | Settings for a bill.
`settings.autopay` | Whether or not payments are scheduled automatically.